Package com.complexible.common.openrdf.query

This package contains classes for working with OpenRdf query objects.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BooleanQueryResult
    An analog to TupleQueryResult and GraphQueryResult, this represents the result to a Boolean/Ask query.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractBooleanQueryResultWriter
    BooleanQueryResultWriter base for creating custom writer implementations which throws UnsupportedOperationException exceptions for the non-boolean result format methods which are incorrectly in the QueryResultWriter interface.
    AbstractQueryResultWriter
    More useful base for creating custom QueryResultWriter implementations.
    BooleanQueryResultImpl
    Default implementation of a BooleanQueryResult
    DelegatingBindingSet
    DelegatingGraphQueryResult
    Base class for creating a GraphQueryResult decorator which delegates all calls to the child result.
    DelegatingTupleQueryResult
    Base class for creating a TupleQueryResult decorator which delegates all calls to its child TupleQueryResult
    ImmutableBindingSet
    An immutable BindingSet
    ImmutableDataset
    A Dataset implementation which is immutable
    ImmutableDataset.ImmutableDatasetBuilder  
    SesameQueryUtils
    Collection of utility methods for working with the OpenRdf Sesame Query API.

Package com.complexible.common.openrdf.query Description

This package contains classes for working with OpenRdf query objects. It includes utilities for rendering, building, modifying, and executing SPARQL & SeRQL queries.
